Thank you everyone for coming yesterday and Congrats to founders @jennieripps @marialienne and meeee!!

#ProudtobeAsian @therealdaytime

node.text:
As we were doing this interview on why we must unite to fight hate, the AAPI community and #NAACP joined forces in ATL today. I am moved to tears seeing the multitude of people from all different backgrounds gather to demand change. This is just the beginning. @IMajorWish thank you for this beautiful photo and  @georgia_NAACP & @NAACP I STAND WITH YOU.

@AlexWittnews thank you for covering our news and so much love to @margaret_cho and @A3pcon Manjusha Kulkarni

node.text:
#StopAsianHate is partnering up with @GoFundMe to have a central destination to fundraise for grassroots AAPI organizations across the nation.  Every donation will support organizations that empower the APPI community and will include initiatives to increase community safety and support for those affected by violence. 

Please take a moment to visit gofundme.com/AAPI to help create change.

Thank you @goldhouseco @gofundme @capeusa @therealphilliplim and @bingchen for organizing.

Eeeeek happy dance🙃
Shooting for #JeannieMaiCollection coming this October. Lotsa yummy layers for fall hunnay!! ❤️🎉

user.full_name: A N G E L A | R Y E

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jeannie Mai Jenkins 💍 on July 19, 2021 tagging @theowlsbrew, and @partnersincrafting. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Still buzzin from our first @theowlsbrew soirée in #LA! Becoming a co-founder of #BoozyTea has been the most exhilarating experience.. to support founders @jennieripps and @marialienne in uplifting women business everywhere. Thank you everyone who made it out, (inc our tea leaf reader, Patty, & owl, Archie🦉❤️) and Mai Fam who continue to send me pics of #OwlsBrew when you’re enjoying it! We’ve officially sold over a million cans, check out theOwlsBrew.com to enter your location and find #BoozyTea near you! 🫖🙃❤️

node.text: Tomorrow I’m honored to be a part of #BeLove Day, a virtual event hosted by the incredible @berniceaking. This day is all about letting go of hatred and making love the new norm - in an effort to unite our society and create lasting change. Please join me, @danieldaekim, @thatdanielwu, @joseiswriting, @lee_minjin and many others as we come together to discuss this revolution ♥️ to learn more, check out @thekingcenter or thekingcenter.org, and tune in tomorrow at 1:30PST/4:30pm EDT on IG Live to join the discussion.
